<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Prompt Input</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/js/prompt.js" defer></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container-box {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            gap: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .prompt-container {
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0d3b66;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .input-group {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .submit-btn, .btn-outline-primary, .btn-outline-danger {
            background-color: #0d3b66;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover, .btn-outline-primary:hover, .btn-outline-danger:hover {
            background-color: #0b3157;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .btn-group {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
        }

        .prompt-textarea {
            resize: none;
            height: 90px;
        }

        .loading-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            z-index: 9999;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .spinner {
            border: 4px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-top: 4px solid #0d3b66;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="btn-group">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/result-list.html'">My Images</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-danger" onclick="window.location.href='/index.html'">Logout</button>
    </div>

    <div class="container-box">
        <div class="prompt-container">
            <div class="title">클라우드운영센터 이미지 생성기</div>
            <div class="description">프롬프트에 원하는 이미지를 텍스트로 요청하세요.</div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <textarea id="promptInput" class="form-control prompt-textarea" placeholder="Describe the image you want..." rows="3"></textarea>
                <button class="btn submit-btn" onclick="submitPrompt()">AI 이미지 생성</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="loadingOverlay" class="loading-overlay">
        Generating image... Please wait
        <div class="spinner"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

